    "• DC3: Model Alignment (T1, T2).",
    "Having good interpretability for the presented topics and keywords is essential to support sensemaking, which is enabled by carefully considering Model Alignment.",
    "Our choice of models should align well with the user's mental model when conducting the analysis tasks for better interpretability.",
